cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on creating 3D models of the environment for autonomous tasks. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper deals with range sensors and 3D reconstructions. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as statistical models are used to perform the reconstructions. Finally, Graphics (cs.GR) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with creating 3D models.
